{"title":"Jupyter和conda协同工作环境搭建和常见错误处理","date":"2019-10-03T00:00:00.000Z","link":"python/jupyter","tags":["conda","jupyter"],"updated":"2022-04-27T15:24:01.731Z","content":"<h1 id=\"避坑安装方法\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"python/jupyter#避坑安装方法\"></a> 避坑安装方法<a href=\"python/jupyter#避坑安装方法\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>如果您还没有安装jupyter notebook，那么按照如下方法可以让jupyter和conda协同工作</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 在base环境下</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安装jupyter本体</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">pip install jupyter</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安装nb_jupyter</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">pip install nb_conda</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 完成</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>好啦，开始使用就完事辣~</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"关于其他方法安装导致故障的原因和修复\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"python/jupyter#关于其他方法安装导致故障的原因和修复\"></a> 关于其他方法安装导致故障的原因和修复<a href=\"python/jupyter#关于其他方法安装导致故障的原因和修复\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"方法a\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"python/jupyter#方法a\"></a> 方法a<a href=\"python/jupyter#方法a\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>安装ipykernel：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda install ipykernel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在虚拟环境下创建kernel文件：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda install -n [环境名] ipykernel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>激活conda环境：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">source activate [环境名]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>将环境写入notebook的kernel中</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python -m ipykernel install --user --name[环境名] --display-name &quot;[显示名])&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"fix\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"python/jupyter#fix\"></a> Fix<a href=\"python/jupyter#fix\"></a></h3>\n<p>环境配置列表在<code>%userprofile%\\Appdata\\Roaming\\jupyter\\kernels\\[环境名]\\kernel.json</code>下，手动修正即可</p>\n<h3 id=\"调试思路\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"python/jupyter#调试思路\"></a> 调试思路<a href=\"python/jupyter#调试思路\"></a></h3>\n<p>conda的工作就是更换环境变量，可以使用<code>sys.path</code>查看conda是否正常工作</p>\n","prev":{"title":"编译原理小结","link":"Review/CompilationPrinciple"},"next":{"title":"共享Jupyter notebook环境","link":"python/jupyterShare"},"plink":"ilucia.github.io/python/jupyter/","toc":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 避坑安装方法","id":"避坑安装方法","index":"1"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 关于其他方法安装导致故障的原因和修复","id":"关于其他方法安装导致故障的原因和修复","index":"2","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 方法a","id":"方法a","index":"2.1","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> Fix","id":"fix","index":"2.1.1"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 调试思路","id":"调试思路","index":"2.1.2"}]}]}],"copyright":{"author":"Ilucia Niu","license":"<a rel=\"license\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">知识共享署名 4.0 国际许可协议</a>","published":"2019年10月3日","updated":"2022年4月27日"}}